INSERT INTO `wp_rg_lead_detail_long` VALUES("285", "The software will provide direct accounting of the number of people attending daily yoga classes, by digitizing the way people sign in and enabling people to pay for classes at the yoga class via credit card and online before they arrive.  It will also allow people to register for yoga school workshops online - by clicking through on our website.  There is an automation for marketing that helps to gain retention with new students, and also reminding regular students when there class cards or monthly memberships have run out. \r\n\r\nJennifer has worked with this software and set it up in MANY STUDIOS.  It is the industry standard.  It\'s easy to customize, easy to use.   It\'s also will be easy now to track how teachers are doing pulling in students from the community, so we can make better decisions on giving teachers more classes, or taking classes off the schedule that are not doing well. \r\n\r\nA merchant account through mind body is set up and all monies will go into the YSNY, with appropriate transfers being made into the ISEWU.  Reports will be run on a weekly basis, much like a credit card statement and Nikki will sit with Laura our bookkeeper to reconcile all accounts.  It\'s very seamless.  It can also happen the opposite way if you wish, will all monies going into the ISEWU and then being transferred into YSNY.  It\'s totally up to Eve!\r\n\r\nAlso, the Yoga School will be paying for the software fully.  Eve is already in on the loop as far as the merchant service account and Laura is happy to do the reconciling as needed.");
